comments: Jade is FANTASTIC! She is honest, raw, and intimidating. With that said, Professor Aguilar is also extremely approachable and incredibly clear at explaining the material for her courses. TAKE JADE IF YOU CAN!

comments: I learned almost nothing in this class. Though attendance is supposed to be mandatory, I honestly felt as if I could have missed every class and still aced the two tests. This class doesn\'t require you to think, just to regurgitate what you have read. Aguilar\'s teaching methods are rather ineffective, perhaps attributable to her inexperience.

comments: Professor Aguilar is a great teacher. At first the workload seemed like a lot but I realized that as long as you do it she will give you a good grade. Class discussion was very interesting! The more you participate in this class the more you will get out of it.

comments: Great class! I don\'t believe everything taught I read or heard but I learned so much! Jade is a GREAT prof. She is understanding,and knowledgeable. This is the most interactive class on W.U.\'s campus! Reading: moderate Writing: Moderate Final project: Challenging and interesting. Like all of life, you get out of it what you only put in to it!
